  <name>Unvanquished</name>
  <summary>A fast paced, first person strategy game</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Unvanquished is a strategy game played on the first person.
      Become a marine, handle your big weapon and dress that
      impressive exoskeleton to save the human race like a boss. Or if
      you prefer, be a monstrous beast and save those cute grangers
      from those two-legged invaders who only know how to turn
      beautiful organic equilibrium into lifeless machines and dead
      concreted worlds.
    </p>
  </description>

